data.description: Duplex with great potential as an investment opportunity in the centrally located Los Angeles Heights community, convenient to I-10 and plenty of shopping and dining options. The downstairs floor plan features an open, spacious living room, a kitchen with plenty of cabinetry, 1 bedroom and 1 bath. The upstairs unit features a spacious kitchen, 2 bedrooms and 1 bath and original wood floors!  Large yard, with so much potential!   No Assignments.
